little_car

Class Components

  • java.lang.Object
    • little_car.Components
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Car, Obstacle

    public class Components
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the superclass for Car and Obstacle The four attributes define the coordinates of the shape to be filled (xPos, yPos) and its dimensions (width, height) All attributes are private and child classes can access them only through the Accessors methods
